Brave women leading #ArewaMeeToo movement, fighting to bring to justice sexual violators have been receiving threats, bullying online & other forms of intimidation. The arrest of Maryam Awaisu @Ice131Queen by a Special Anti-Robbery Squad (SARS) of @PoliceNG is part of wider intimidation.
@#ArewaMeeToo...it's is a pity how the legal system choose to protect the Perpetrators of child sexual abuse & molestation instead of protecting the right of a child!
